    "detail": "<p>国内用的人不多 在Twitter问了官方说采用的是SM-5间隔重复算法，对于闪卡只有「Forgotten」、「Remember」和「Took a while to recall」三档</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8b92f84ab86b10de518ebf059d197752_b.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"3360\" data-rawheight=\"1712\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"3360\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8b92f84ab86b10de518ebf059d197752_r.jpg\"/><figcaption>Logseq 闪卡功能</figcaption></figure><p>而不是像anki一样「忘记」「困难」「良好」「简单」四档选择</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c177c1cb928a1ac280f9a94e2d1ff785_b.jpg\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1334\" data-rawheight=\"1184\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1334\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c177c1cb928a1ac280f9a94e2d1ff785_r.jpg\"/><figcaption>Anki闪卡对记忆程度的四档分级</figcaption></figure><p>相较于anki，少了一档的logseq对内容记忆程度分级是否更笼统了？会因此影响记忆项的复习频率，最终影响记忆效果吗？</p><p>Logseq is a local-first, non-linear, outliner notebook for organizing and sharing your personal knowledge base.</p><p>Use it to organize your todo list, to write your journals, or to record your unique life.</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/logseq/logseq\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"visible\">github.com/logseq/logse</span><span class=\"invisible\">q</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a><p></p>",
